    <title>Conflux.Paginize</title>
    <authors>Conflux Development Team</authors>
    <owners>Conflux</owners>
    <description>A comprehensive pagination library for .NET applications supporting multi-column sorting for both IQueryable and IEnumerable data sources. Features a clean Filter-based API for better parameter management.</description>
    <releaseNotes>
      Initial release featuring:
      - Filter-based API for clean parameter management
      - Multi-column sorting support for IQueryable and IEnumerable
      - Dynamic column sorting with reflection
      - Case-insensitive column name support
      - Automatic parameter validation and correction
      - Comprehensive error handling and edge case management
      - Performance optimizations with property caching
      - Extensive test coverage with 30+ unit tests
      - Built-in validation attributes for Filter class
      - Support for all common data types (string, numeric, DateTime, bool, etc.)
    </releaseNotes>
    <summary>Advanced pagination and sorting library for .NET applications with Filter-based API</summary>
